u received a bronze medal on Aug. 16.\", \"from\": 3993, \"to\": 4036, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"B\\u0103rbosu\", \"from\": 3993, \"to\": 4000}, {\"ngram\": \"a bronze medal\", \"from\": 4010, \"to\": 4024}, {\"ngram\": \"Aug.\", \"from\": 4028, \"to\": 4032}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking to reporters after the ceremony, B\\u0103rbosu said that the controversy was \\\"saddening\\\" and that she was sending U.S. gymnasts \\\"good thoughts.\\\"\", \"from\": 4038, \"to\": 4185, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"reporters\", \"from\": 4050, \"to\": 4059}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 4066, \"to\": 4078}, {\"ngram\": \"B\\u0103rbosu\", \"from\": 4080, \"to\": 4087}, {\"ngram\": \"the controversy\", \"from\": 4098, \"to\": 4113}, {\"ngram\": \"U.S. gymnasts\", \"from\": 4155, \"to\": 4168}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"good thoughts\", \"from\": 4169, \"to\": 4183}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am thinking of them even if today I got the medal,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 4187, \"to\": 4251, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the medal\", \"from\": 4230, \"to\": 4239}]}, {\"sentence\": \"B\\u0103rbosu added that \\\"we expected the referees and staff at the Olympics to do their job properly.\\\"\", \"from\": 4253, \"to\": 4350, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"B\\u0103rbosu\", \"from\": 4253, \"to\": 4260}, {\"ngram\": \"the referees\", \"from\": 4285, \"to\": 4297}, {\"ngram\": \"staff\", \"from\": 4302, \"to\": 4307}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4311, \"to\": 4323}, {\"ngram\": \"their job\", \"from\": 4330, \"to\": 4339}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Aug. 10, Chiles shared three broken-heart emoji on her Instagram story, writing in a subsequent message that she would be \\\"taking this time and removing myself from social media\\\" for her mental health.\", \"from\": 4352, \"to\": 4556, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4410, \"end\": 4419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1747787845961082e-44, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Aug.\", \"from\": 4355, \"to\": 4359}, {\"ngram\": \"Chiles\", \"from\": 4364, \"to\": 4370}, {\"ngram\": \"three broken-heart emoji\", \"from\": 4378, \"to\": 4402}, {\"ngram\": \"a subsequent message\", \"from\": 4438, \"to\": 4458}, {\"ngram\": \"this time\", \"from\": 4485, \"to\": 4494}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 4520, \"to\": 4532}, {\"ngram\": \"her mental health\", \"from\": 4538, \"to\": 4555}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Several days later, on Aug. 15, Chiles issued astatement to Instagramsaying that she was \\\"overwhelmed by the love\\\" she had received and thanked everyone for their support after being stripped of her medal and the court's decision to deny the USAG appeal.\", \"from\": 4558, \"to\": 4812, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4800, \"end\": 4804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USAG\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Aug.\", \"from\": 4581, \"to\": 4585}, {\"ngram\": \"Chiles\", \"from\": 4590, \"to\": 4596}, {\"ngram\": \"astatement\", \"from\": 4604, \"to\": 4614}, {\"ngram\": \"Instagramsaying\", \"from\": 4618, \"to\": 4633}, {\"ngram\": \"the love\", \"from\": 4663, \"to\": 4671}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 4702, \"to\": 4710}, {\"ngram\": \"their support\", \"from\": 4715, \"to\": 4728}, {\"ngram\": \"her medal\", \"from\": 4753, \"to\": 4762}, {\"ngram\": \"the court's decision\", \"from\": 4767, \"to\": 4787}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This decision feels unjust and comes as a significant blow, not just to me, but to everyone who has championed my journey,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 4814, \"to\": 4948, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This decision\", \"from\": 4815, \"to\": 4828}, {\"ngram\": \"a significant blow\", \"from\": 4855, \"to\": 4873}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 4898, \"to\": 4906}, {\"ngram\": \"my journey\", \"from\": 4926, \"to\": 4936}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She also condemned the online attacks she had been subjected to since the ruling, adding that \\\"unprompted racially driven attacks on social media\\\" about her have been \\\"extremely hurtful.\\\"\", \"from\": 4950, \"to\": 5137, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the online attacks\", \"from\": 4969, \"to\": 4987}, {\"ngram\": \"the ruling\", \"from\": 5020, \"to\": 5030}, {\"ngram\": \"racially driven attacks\", \"from\": 5056, \"to\": 5079}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 5083, \"to\": 5095}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have poured my heart and soul into this sport and I am so proud to represent my culture and my country,\\\" she continued.\", \"from\": 5139, \"to\": 5261, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my heart\", \"from\": 5154, \"to\": 5162}, {\"ngram\": \"soul\", \"from\": 5167, \"to\": 5171}, {\"ngram\": \"this sport\", \"from\": 5177, \"to\": 5187}, {\"ngram\": \"my culture\", \"from\": 5219, \"to\": 5229}, {\"ngram\": \"my country\", \"from\": 5234, \"to\": 5244}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will never waver from my values of competing with integrity, striving for excellence, upholding the values of sportsmanship and the rules that dictate fairness.\\\"\", \"from\": 5262, \"to\": 5426, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my values\", \"from\": 5287, \"to\": 5296}, {\"ngram\": \"integrity\", \"from\": 5315, \"to\": 5324}, {\"ngram\": \"excellence\", \"from\": 5339, \"to\": 5349}, {\"ngram\": \"the values\", \"from\": 5361, \"to\": 5371}, {\"ngram\": \"sportsmanship\", \"from\": 5375, \"to\": 5388}, {\"ngram\": \"the rules\", \"from\": 5393, \"to\": 5402}, {\"ngram\": \"fairness\", \"from\": 5416, \"to\": 5424}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Nov. 11,Chiles gave her first live TV interviewsince thescoring controversyon TODAY, telling Hoda Kotb that she now feels \\\"comfortable\\\" to talk about her experience.\", \"from\": 5428, \"to\": 5596, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5524, \"end\": 5533, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_Kotb\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hoda Kotb\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_Kotb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_Kotb\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nov.\", \"from\": 5431, \"to\": 5435}, {\"ngram\": \"her first live TV interviewsince thescoring controversyon\", \"from\": 5451, \"to\": 5508}, {\"ngram\": \"her experience\", \"from\": 5581, \"to\": 5595}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Honestly, it's been really, really hard just to comprehend everything that's been happening,\\\" Chiles said, becoming emotional.\", \"from\": 5598, \"to\": 5725, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 5658, \"to\": 5668}, {\"ngram\": \"Chiles\", \"from\": 5693, \"to\": 5699}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have been able to finally now feel comfortable in a way to talk about what has been happening.\", \"from\": 5726, \"to\": 5823, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 5779, \"to\": 5784}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u2026 it's just been a difficult time for myself and I am ready to speak on my truth.\\\"\", \"from\": 5824, \"to\": 5906, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a difficult time\", \"from\": 5841, \"to\": 5857}, {\"ngram\": \"my truth\", \"from\": 5896, \"to\": 5904}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She continued, \\\"I think now, it's just the support that's been around me that I have been like, 'OK, I can not control anything that's happening on the outside, I can only control what my truth is, and I know what the truth is, and I know that we were right in everything that we were doing.'\\\"\", \"from\": 5908, \"to\": 6201, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the support\", \"from\": 5947, \"to\": 5958}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 6027, \"to\": 6035}, {\"ngram\": \"the outside\", \"from\": 6056, \"to\": 6067}, {\"ngram\": \"my truth\", \"from\": 6093, \"to\": 6101}, {\"ngram\": \"the truth\", \"from\": 6122, \"to\": 6131}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 6169, \"to\": 6179}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chiles said her late grandfather's memory has given her strength over the last several months, recalling advice he'd given her: \\\"'Everything happens for a reason.\", \"from\": 6203, \"to\": 6365, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chiles\", \"from\": 6203, \"to\": 6209}, {\"ngram\": \"her late grandfather's memory\", \"from\": 6215, \"to\": 6244}, {\"ngram\": \"her strength\", \"from\": 6255, \"to\": 6267}, {\"ngram\": \"the last several months\", \"from\": 6273, \"to\": 6296}, {\"ngram\": \"advice\", \"from\": 6308, \"to\": 6314}, {\"ngram\": \"Everything\", \"from\": 6333, \"to\": 6343}, {\"ngram\": \"a reason\", \"from\": 6356, \"to\": 6364}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is reasons on why you are the person you are.\", \"from\": 6366, \"to\": 6417, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"reasons\", \"from\": 6375, \"to\": 6382}, {\"ngram\": \"the person\", \"from\": 6398, \"to\": 6408}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is reasons on why people look up to you.'\\\"\", \"from\": 6418, \"to\": 6466, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"reasons\", \"from\": 6427, \"to\": 6434}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 6442, \"to\": 6448}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the IOC asked that Chiles return the bronze medal on Aug. 11, the U.S. Olympic & Paralympic Committee (USOPC) said in a statement that they plan to appeal the decision.\", \"from\": 6468, \"to\": 6642, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6478, \"end\": 6481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0175100098454225e-48, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chiles\", \"from\": 6493, \"to\": 6499}, {\"ngram\": \"the bronze medal\", \"from\": 6507, \"to\": 6523}, {\"ngram\": \"Aug.\", \"from\": 6527, \"to\": 6531}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S. Olympic & Paralympic Committee\", \"from\": 6536, \"to\": 6575}, {\"ngram\": \"USOPC\", \"from\": 6577, \"to\": 6582}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 6592, \"to\": 6603}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 6629, \"to\": 6641}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We firmly believe that Jordan rightfully earned the bronze medal, and there were critical errors in both the initial scoring by the International Gymnastics Federation (FIG) and the subsequent CAS appeal process that need to be addressed,\\\" the statement began.\", \"from\": 6644, \"to\": 6905, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6668, \"end\": 6674, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan\", \"score\": 0.9896903229202616, \"rank\": 0.010413727105066536, \"text\": \"Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan\"}, {\"begin\": 6777, \"end\": 6818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Gymnastics_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Gymnastics Federation (FIG)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Gymnastics_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Gymnastics_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 6777, \"end\": 6818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Gymnastics_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Gymnastics Federation (FIG)\", \"types\": [\"Q432